			<description><![CDATA[<p>
	Modu Design Communications is interested in working with an intermediate print and digital freelance designer with 3+ years experience and available to work remotely during regular working hours (9-5).</p>
<p>
	We are a fast-paced team with high-profile clients across a number of industries. Both our clients and ourselves have high standards. Some of our clients include Scene/Cineplex, Manulife Financial, University of Toronto and BMW.</p>
<p>
	Our ideal candidate should be educated in design fundamentals, be technically proficient as outlined below and be able to self-manage. Just as essential, however, they must be able to respond to inquiries quickly, be able to communicate effectively with other team members and adhere to project timelines.</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;</p>
<p>
	<strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
	<li>
		Excellent design layout skills for print and web, a good understanding of</li>
	<li>
		design principles and the ability to conceptualize and execute.</li>
	<li>
		Design/production of print collateral for client projects including booth graphics, flyers, brochures, logos, business cards, and other types of media.</li>
	<li>
		Creating clean HTML and CSS for online projects such as websites, microsites, e-newsletters and banner ads.</li>
	<li>
		Meeting deadlines through project management.</li>
	<li>
		Familiarity of adhering to and understanding corporate brand guidelines.</li>
</ul>
<br />
<p>
	<strong>You must possess the following skills and experience</strong>:</p>
<ul>
	<li>
		3+ years of design experience in an agency setting</li>
	<li>
		3+ years of HTML / CSS coding experience (tableless HTML design)</li>
	<li>
		Strong experience with Adobe Creative Suite programs such as Photoshop, Illustrator, Dreamweaver, and InDesign</li>
	<li>
		Strong knowledge in the use of design concepts (layout, typography, color, white space, and grid and understanding of print concepts (bleed, resolution, and color)</li>
	<li>
		Strong knowledge of HTML5, JavaScript, CSS including Javascript frameworks such as jQuery</li>
	<li>
		Proficiency with cross-browser / cross-platform issues and web standards</li>
	<li>
		Working knowledge of Flash.</li>
</ul>
<p>
	<strong>Experience with the following would be considered an asset:</strong></p>
<ul>
	<li>
		Development with PHP / MySQL</li>
	<li>
		Experience with open source CMS packages such as Wordpress, Joomla or Drupal</li>
	<li>
		Copy writing for client deliverables and corporate communications</li>
	<li>
		Web Analytics using a variety of tools like Google Analytics</li>
	<li>
		Illustration experience</li>
</ul>
<p>
	<br />
	<strong>Provide:</strong></p>
<p>
	Resume<br />
	Provide a portfolio of your work<br />
	2 reference clients to validate your work</p>
